   "id": "779a7d1d-c104-4fee-9432-d79991318778",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Final Reflection\n",
    "\n",
    "## Role of Weights and Biases\n",
    "Weights determine the importance of input features while biases help shift activation values for better predictions.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Why Activation Function is Required\n",
    "Activation functions introduce non-linearity and allow neural networks to learn complex patterns.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Learning Rate Analysis\n",
    "A very high learning rate causes unstable learning, while a very low learning rate slows model training.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Underfitting and Overfitting\n",
    "The model achieved strong testing accuracy without significant signs of underfitting or overfitting."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ce762488-b815-4ee9-b7ca-4321ea126bc8",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Conclusion\n",
    "\n",
    "The neural network model successfully predicted customer churn with high accuracy.\n",
    "\n",
    "Data preprocessing, feature scaling, and hyperparameter tuning significantly improved the model performance.\n",
    "\n",
    "The project demonstrated the practical implementation of neural networks for supervised learning problems."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d9696af9-6527-44ec-8a01-5bb6d0d8158b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Neural Network Training Behavior Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "## Forward Pass\n",
    "During the forward pass, the input features were passed through the hidden layers where weighted computations and activation functions generated predictions.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Loss Calculation\n",
    "The loss function measured the difference between predicted outputs and actual target values during training.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Backpropagation\n",
    "Backpropagation updated the neural network weights and biases by minimizing prediction errors using gradient descent optimization.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Parameter Updates\n",
    "The optimizer continuously adjusted model parameters to improve prediction accuracy over multiple training epochs."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "68f42432-e89a-49ba-ba9f-8a7691d931f8",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Model Architecture Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "Input Layer:\n",
    "The input layer received all processed customer features.\n",
    "\n",
    "Hidden Layer:\n",
    "The neural network used hidden layers with activation functions to learn complex feature relationships.\n",
    "\n",
    "Output Layer:\n",
    "The output layer predicted customer churn probability for binary classification.\n",
    "\n",
    "Optimizer Used:\n",
    "Adam Optimizer\n",
    "\n",
    "Loss Function:\n",
    "Binary Crossentropy\n",
    "\n",
    "Activation Function:\n",
    "ReLU and Tanh"
   ]
  },
